---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Disclosure', url: '/disclosure/' },
];
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate disclosure — WrenchStack"
  description="How WrenchStack makes money and the relationship between affiliate programs and rankings."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Affiliate disclosure</h1>

    <p>
      WrenchStack earns commissions when readers sign up to software platforms through tracked
      links on our pages. The vendor pays the commission from their customer acquisition budget —
      you pay the same price as buying direct.
    </p>

    <h2>Programs we currently work with</h2>

    <p>
      We're an affiliate partner with multiple field service software vendors. The current
      partner roster is published on our <a href="/affiliate-programs/">software partners page</a>.
      We update the list as relationships change.
    </p>

    <h2>How affiliate relationships affect rankings</h2>

    <p>
      Rankings on WrenchStack are produced by the <a href="/methodology/">WrenchStack Score</a> —
      a weighted formula across vertical fit, user ratings, pricing transparency, feature depth,
      and integration coverage. The scoring algorithm has no input field for affiliate commission
      rate. Tools we earn nothing from can rank above tools we earn $10,000 per signup on, and
      regularly do.
    </p>

    <h2>FTC compliance</h2>

    <p>
      WrenchStack complies with the FTC's
      <a href="https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/resources/disclosures-101-social-media-influencers">Endorsement Guides</a>.
      Affiliate links use <code>rel="sponsored"</code> in the page source. Outbound CTAs use
      <code>nofollow noopener</code> for security and search engine signaling.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions</h2>

    <p>
      Email <a href="mailto:hello@wrenchstack.com">hello@wrenchstack.com</a> for corrections or
      clarifications. For vendor partnership inquiries, use <a href="mailto:partners@wrenchstack.com">partners@wrenchstack.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
